{
  "texts": [
    "95 For some ADM systems, the opposite is true.",
    "Consider the case of iBorderCtrl, an EU-funded project developing a technology for lie detection based on emotion recognition.",
    "The project envisaged a two-step procedure.",
    "Before travelling to Europe, people would be asked to answer questions in front of a video camera.",
    "On arrival at the EU borders, their recorded facial expressions would be compared with pictures from the previous border crossing."
  ]
}